Module mesakit.map.road.name.parser
Package com.telenav.mesakit.map.road.name.parser.tokenizer

Class Tokenizer

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.mesakit.map.road.name.parser.tokenizer.Tokenizer
Direct Known Subclasses:
EnglishTokenizer, IndonesianTokenizer
public class Tokenizer extends Object
Returns a list of tokens given an input string. Note that there may be more than one symbol in a token, for example "NORTH WEST" is three symbols in a row: NORTH, WHITESPACE and WEST.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
